verbatim_text:
The elaboration of the « Citizen Awareness Promotion Plan - CAPP » is meant to educate and inform the local population and stakeholders.

It could encompass several actions, including:

- The creation of a permanent municipal information point;
- The organisation of an open house;
- The publication of articles in local and regional newspapers;
- The distribution of brochures and posters; and
- The distribution of an information letter that includes current events on sustainability as well as local success stories.
